---
import "@fontsource/quicksand";
---

<style lang="scss">
  @use "sass:color";
  $primary: rgba(256, 256, 256, 1);
  $accent: rgba(251, 198, 200, 1);
  $bg: rgba(0, 0, 0, 1);

  body {
    background-color: $bg;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    color: $primary;
    font-family: "Quicksand";
    main {
      width: 65ch;
      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        color: color.change($accent, $alpha: 0.5);
      }
      p {
        margin-bottom: 1em;
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: color.change($primary, $alpha: 0.5);
      }
      span {
        color: color.change($accent, $alpha: 0.5)
      }
      hr {
        border-color: color.change($accent, $alpha: 0.25);
        width: 25%;
      }
    }
  }
</style>

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
    <title>Kyuu Iota</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <h1>Kyuu Iota</h1>
      <p>
        Hey I'm Kyuu Iota, a passionate <span>backend engineer</span> with a focus
        on building robust, efficient and reliable web applications. With my
        <span
          >{
            Math.floor(
              (new Date().getTime() - new Date(2020, 7, 7).getTime()) /
                31557600000
            )
          } years of experience</span
        > in programming and development, I have fostered a deep expertise in crafting
        robust solutions.
      </p>
      <p>
        I specialize in developing server-side architecture, api integrations,
        database management, and optimizing performance of existing
        applications. I have a comprehensive grasp on programming languages such
        as <span>typescript</span> & <span>rust</span> and frameworks such as
        <span>next.js</span>, <span>astro</span>, <span>prisma</span>,
        <span>tailwindcss</span>, <span>axum</span> & <span>warp</span>
        allowing me to deliver optimal solutions for a diverse array of challenges.
        <p>
          In addition to my technical knowledge, I prioritize principles of
          <span>clean code</span> & development of maintanable solutions. I have
          a strong emphasis on writing code that is efficient and effective while
          also prioritizing organization and clarity. I am strongly committed to
          <span>continuous learning</span>, staying updated on the latest
          industry trends, and constantly expanding my knowledge and skills.
        </p>
        <p>
          Feel free to reach out to me through the contact information provided.
        </p>
        <hr />
      </p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
